'''特洛伊学区'''<ref>"[http://www.oakland.k12.mi.us/china/China_one.pdf 2007 Oakland Schools Chinese Language & Culture Initiative]{{dead link|date=2018年3月 |bot=InternetArchiveBot |fix-attempted=yes }}." [[Oakland_Schools|Oakland Schools]]. June 2007.</ref>（Troy School District）是[[密歇根|密歇根]]县的学区，总部在[[特洛伊_(密歇根州)|特洛伊]]。


特洛伊学区是在1950年由几个前学区合并而成的<ref>{{Cite web |url=https://www.troyhistoricvillage.org/november-15-the-consolidation-of-troy-schools/ |title=article on formation of Troy School district |access-date=2021-08-29 |archive-date=2021-05-20 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210520184009/https://www.troyhistoricvillage.org/november-15-the-consolidation-of-troy-schools/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>。2004年3月，该学区提出了一项119美元的债券，将建造一所新的国际学校，为贝克中学提供一个替代设施，并升级设施技术，以换取20年内增加0.99毫米的财产税。投票定于2004年6月14日举行<ref>"[http://nl.newsbank.com/nl-search/we/Archives?p_product=DTNB&s_site=detnews&f_site=detnews&f_sitename=Detroit+News%2C+The+%28MI%29&p_multi=DTNB&p_theme=gannett&p_action=search&p_maxdocs=200&p_topdoc=1&p_text_direct-0=1017C183E47EA2B2&p_field_direct-0=document_id&p_perpage=10&p_sort=YMD_date:D&s_trackval=GooglePM  Troy district pushes $119 million projects bond] {{Wayback|url=http://nl.newsbank.com/nl-search/we/Archives?p_product=DTNB&s_site=detnews&f_site=detnews&f_sitename=Detroit+News%2C+The+%28MI%29&p_multi=DTNB&p_theme=gannett&p_action=search&p_maxdocs=200&p_topdoc=1&p_text_direct-0=1017C183E47EA2B2&p_field_direct-0=document_id&p_perpage=10&p_sort=YMD_date:D&s_trackval=GooglePM |date=20210829083115 }}." ''[[The_Detroit_News|The Detroit News]]''. March 21, 2004. Retrieved on September 9, 2013. ID number det18520650.</ref>。

特洛伊学区营运十二所小学、四所初中、四所高中，学生人数达多于12,000人。<ref>"[http://www.troy.k12.mi.us/files/_nIAs0_/8da28d76659fa6113745a49013852ec4/TSD_Annual_Report_2011.12.pdf 2011-2012 Annual Report]{{dead link|date=2018年3月 |bot=InternetArchiveBot |fix-attempted=yes }}." 特洛伊学区. p. 6. "More than 12,000 students are enrolled in twelve elementary, four middle schools and two traditional and one non traditional high school."</ref>

